# SkyWeb Change Log

## 2026-06-08 — DN-9.4 Alert Overlays and Chart Annotations

- Added chart alert overlay plumbing in the .NET-lane client.
- Indicator detail charts can now load matching active indicator alert rules and annotate thresholds/events when the user is signed in.
- Macro-view detail charts can now load matching active view-metric alert rules and annotate selected series with relevant thresholds/events.
- Added reusable alert overlay adapter helpers for threshold normalization, alert event/notification mapping, metric-key filtering, and overlay counts.
- Extended the reusable ECharts chart option builders with severity-aware threshold mark lines and alert event scatter markers.
- Added a chart-level alert overlay toggle and meta-strip overlay count.
- Hardened alert tooltip rendering with escaped alert event messages.

